snippet.title: Ega Trek gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Ega Trek, Dos PC game produced by Nels Anderson in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/ega-trek/4000/
Ega Trek really is a fine little game, you race around the galaxy trying to survive or even get a high score. You can explore different sectors in space, each with there own planets, enemies and friends.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
